"2017-08-31T22:05:54.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"5e940879ca5ea2ec905344ddf4747530dc5c6c8c","tid":382612,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em><span style=\"color: green;\">首先要有個拍左拖好耐嘅on9女朋友一直原諒。</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我朋友拍左超過5年嘅仆街男朋友無啦啦搵一大堆籍口同佢講分手，事後先發現條仆街偷食，但條仆街係我朋友面前唔認。<br />\n但轉頭就post ig 自爆，話會對第三者專一。<br />\n我忍無可忍決定爆佢大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/222839_28c218cd54d929cefeb0764796c98ba4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F222839_28c218cd54d929cefeb0764796c98ba4.jpg&h=18c461c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/222839_a9438d84edf84d4fe661d64447e16277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F222839_a9438d84edf84d4fe661d64447e16277.jpg&h=458395b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/230734_2d0f625cde210f87dc927e14a4214006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F230734_2d0f625cde210f87dc927e14a4214006.jpg&h=d110b912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新女唔知自己係第三者 所以唔出樣啦<br />\n佢同我女仔朋友（簡稱A)有私下聯絡過。<br />\n新女得知條仆街有其他女，又成日蒲，又偷食過，又唔想做第三者，就同佢講分手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/212418_b7f5613d6edfc3ab972b3d2e1021dbe3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F212418_b7f5613d6edfc3ab972b3d2e1021dbe3.JPG&h=18148e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係條仔一邊向新女箍煲，一邊向A 箍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/211224_414adcc8b6a49505336cc71ce8dded29.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F211224_414adcc8b6a49505336cc71ce8dded29.JPG&h=020301c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/211225_5ffb805a9b1c8029e8a817b4bd3618d5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F211225_5ffb805a9b1c8029e8a817b4bd3618d5.JPG&h=87525b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/225948_931fda0e460c3be0324c3407572e0a6b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F225948_931fda0e460c3be0324c3407572e0a6b.jpeg&h=ad560d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/212502_b47da97c555b4464f5856d732c384314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F212502_b47da97c555b4464f5856d732c384314.JPG&h=7283caa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後新女都話想同條仆街分手，仲搵到條仔係同A一齊期間同另一女偷食嘅證據。 (條仆街話自己一腳踏兩船，其實好撚多船⁠⁠⁠⁠)<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/222550_cbd75b92a66f1616c372280eff3a7862.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F222550_cbd75b92a66f1616c372280eff3a7862.jpeg&d=NupbHYB5KW%2FHdrkWaglYOPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=77e0eee8\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/222550_cbd75b92a66f1616c372280eff3a7862.jpeg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/221533_a79556c30faed720e500fb382fcf62a3.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F221533_a79556c30faed720e500fb382fcf62a3.jpeg&d=NupbHYB5KW%2FHdrkWaglYOPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dfa29baa\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/221533_a79556c30faed720e500fb382fcf62a3.jpeg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/235248_b